No. —. Original.

Ex parte. In the Matter of Helen Post, Petitioner. Submitted May 4, 1903. Decided June 1, 1903. Mr. H. Bisbee and Mr. George C. Bedell for petitioner. Mr. Assistant General Purdy opposing. Per Curiam.

Motion for leave to file petition for a writ of habeas corpus denied, on the authority of Ex parte Mirzan, 119 U. S. 584; In re Chapman, 156 U. S. 211; In re Belt, 159 U. S. 95.
